I am using this video from now on to explain to people how my brain works. When you ask me a question, I don’t go this deep. I maybe go about 10-15 minutes deep (as opposed to Michael’s 21 minutes) and I compress my 10-15 minutes into 5-7 minutes, which for most people is 4-6 minutes too much information, BUT it is less than half of what I was thinking and not nearly as complex as Michael from Vsauce.

I am a 10-15 minute guy, dumbing things down to 5-7 minutes, living in a 30 second world.
